name: Elf of Era
description:
Elf of Era(a. k. a. EOE) Group is a virtual idol girl group under Yuehua Entertainment.
It consists of 5 members: Tang Waner, Bai Luzao, An Minuo, Su Yumo, and Jiang Youen.
They will create positive energy for everyone through interactive live broadcasts, stage performances, and content creation.
> Five passionate young girls dream of being the ghostly elves who sow happiness in this era. On the way of pursuing their dreams, no matter whether it is the stars or the wind and frost, they can't be stopped.
